description:
Kate has an exciting new High-Low product comparison to share, and Doree deals with a broken computer. Then, Project Runway winner and fashion designer Ashley Nell Tipton joins them to talk about her skincare favorites, her experiences as a plus-size designer, and how her definition of self-love changed after winning Project Runway.


We’re breaking down the best cleansers and want to know your favorite. Tell us here!


To leave a voicemail or text for a future episode, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
